TERMS OF SERVICE FOR ASHLEY MUSIC BOT

LAST UPDATED: NOVEMBER 2025

1. ACCEPTANCE OF TERMS

BY INVITING, USING, OR INTERACTING WITH ASHLEY MUSIC BOT (“THE BOT”), YOU AGREE TO THESE TERMS OF SERVICE (“TERMS”). IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THESE TERMS, DO NOT USE THE BOT.

2. DESCRIPTION OF SERVICE

ASHLEY MUSIC BOT PROVIDES MUSIC STREAMING AND ENTERTAINMENT FEATURES WITHIN THE DISCORD PLATFORM. THE BOT IS DESIGNED TO PLAY AUDIO FROM VARIOUS SOURCES IN VOICE CHANNELS AND MAY INCLUDE ADDITIONAL FUNCTIONS SUCH AS QUEUE MANAGEMENT, PLAYLISTS, AND USER COMMANDS.

3. USER RESPONSIBILITY

USERS MUST COMPLY WITH DISCORD’S TERMS OF SERVICE AND COMMUNITY GUIDELINES AT ALL TIMES.

USERS SHALL NOT USE THE BOT FOR ANY UNLAWFUL, HARMFUL, OR DISRUPTIVE PURPOSES.

USERS ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR THE CONTENT THEY REQUEST, SHARE, OR STREAM THROUGH THE BOT.

THE BOT OWNER IS NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR ACTIONS TAKEN BY USERS WHILE USING THE BOT.

4. DATA COLLECTION AND PRIVACY

ASHLEY MUSIC BOT MAY STORE BASIC DATA SUCH AS USER IDS, GUILD IDS, AND SETTINGS REQUIRED FOR FUNCTIONALITY.

NO PERSONAL INFORMATION BEYOND DISCORD’S PUBLIC USER DATA IS COLLECTED.

DATA IS NEVER SOLD OR SHARED WITH THIRD PARTIES.

USERS MAY REQUEST DATA DELETION BY CONTACTING THE BOT OWNER DIRECTLY.

5. SERVICE AVAILABILITY

THE BOT IS PROVIDED “AS IS” AND “AS AVAILABLE.”

THERE IS NO GUARANTEE OF UPTIME OR CONTINUOUS OPERATION.

THE BOT OWNER MAY MODIFY, UPDATE, OR DISCONTINUE ANY FEATURE OR THE ENTIRE SERVICE AT ANY TIME WITHOUT NOTICE.

6. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY

UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES SHALL THE BOT OWNER OR DEVELOPERS BE HELD LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES, LOSSES, OR DISRUPTIONS RESULTING FROM THE USE OR INABILITY TO USE THE BOT.

7. PROHIBITED USES

USERS SHALL NOT:

USE THE BOT TO STREAM COPYRIGHTED MATERIAL WITHOUT PERMISSION.

ATTEMPT TO MODIFY, REVERSE ENGINEER, OR EXPLOIT THE BOT’S CODE.

USE THE BOT FOR RAIDING, SPAMMING, OR HARASSING OTHER USERS OR SERVERS.

8. TERMINATION OF SERVICE

THE BOT OWNER RESERVES THE RIGHT TO REMOVE THE BOT FROM ANY SERVER OR BAN USERS WITHOUT PRIOR NOTICE IF THESE TERMS ARE VIOLATED.

9. OWNERSHIP AND INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

ALL CODE, DESIGN, BRANDING, AND FUNCTIONALITY OF ASHLEY MUSIC BOT ARE THE PROPERTY OF ITS OWNER AND ARE PROTECTED UNDER APPLICABLE COPYRIGHT AND INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY LAWS.

10. CHANGES TO TERMS

THE BOT OWNER MAY UPDATE THESE TERMS AT ANY TIME. CONTINUED USE OF THE BOT AFTER CHANGES ARE MADE CONSTITUTES ACCEPTANCE OF THE NEW TERMS.

11. CONTACT INFORMATION

FOR QUESTIONS OR CONCERNS REGARDING THESE TERMS, PLEASE CONTACT THE BOT OWNER THROUGH THE OFFICIAL SUPPORT SERVER OR DESIGNATED CHANNELS.

BY USING ASHLEY MUSIC BOT, YOU CONFIRM THAT YOU HAVE READ, UNDERSTOOD, AND AGREED TO THESE TERMS OF SERVICE IN FULL.
